{"type": "article", "id": 23871, "title": "骨灰花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607103901dsLkpWzweP7DHS18.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个白色的花瓶是一个孵化器，设计师的想法是将骨灰放在其中，通过自然降解滋养植物。花瓶有两层，中间含有储水系统，可以通过特殊装置自动浇水。他们认为对逝者缅怀的最好方式是看到回归自然和新生，这也是一种经济环保的方式。西班牙的设计师早在 1997 年就提出了，直到 2013 年才生产出产品，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/biosurn/bios-incube-the-worlds-first-incubator-for-the-aft\">它目前正在众筹。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103858Q25t9ZKO0XaNdYWU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103859TSdVwmEJgbly5t6H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103859bCs4jMVl2vcPzGdL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103900mH30hOuAyKDfUkY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103900iVJzawoAUgZqTt8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}